                    Supplier rating is carried out once in a 3 month as given bellow.<br />
                    [a] Quality Rating (RQ) :<br />

                    RQ = [(Q1x1+Q3x0.75) / N] x100<br />
                    Where as, N = Total Quantity Supplied<br />
                    Q1 = Total Quantity accepted<br />
                    Q3 = Total Quantity rejected<br />
                    [b] Delivery Rating (RT) :<br />
                    RT = [(T1 + T2x0.5)/N]x100<br />
                    Where as, N  = Total ok quantity supplied<br />
                    T1 = Total quantity supplied within time<br />
                    T2 = Total quantity supplied late<br />
                    [C] Overall Rating (R) :<br />
                    R = [RQ + RT] / 2<br />
                    Rating grade :<br />
                    A = Above 90.0%<br />
                    B = 80% to 90%<br />
                    C = 70% to 79.9%<br />
